<includeonly>{| class="wikitable source-semanticschemas"
{{Category/display-header | category={{{category|}}} | label={{{label|}}} }}</includeonly><noinclude>
Opens the top half of a SemanticSchemas category display wikitable:
the `{|` frame plus the heading row (via `Category/display-header`).
Pairs with `Category/table-footer` to bracket a sequence of
`Category/property-row` (and optionally `Category/backlink-row`) calls.

Parameters:
* category - The category name (without namespace prefix). Required.
* label    - Optional baked display label. Forwarded to
             `Category/display-header`.
</noinclude>
